How do subscriptions work?

Description

The Pet Vogue BONE SHAPED RUBBER CHEW TOY made from all-natural food-grade rubber and is BPA-free, safe and very durable for your Small pet chewing and playing.

    Key Features:

    • TOOTH CLEANING: Keep your dog busy, happy, and satisfied with chew toys, The raised thorns spread all over to increase the force of friction, to help clean teeth and massage gums, improve oral health and discomforts from teething.this dental bone is suitable for all dogs and puppies and is a safe, gentle, and effective way to care for your dog's teeth.
    • REDUCES ANXIETY AND BOREDOM: Dog Chew toys teaches good chewing habits while satisfying the natural urge to chew and reduces their anxiety and boredom. To avoid dog bite shoes, sofa, desk, and chair because of tusks right out, assembly unnecessary damage.
    • SATISFACTION GUARANTEED: Designed to help freshen breath, stimulate gums, and reduce tartar and plaque buildup as your dog plays and chews away.
